::DarkMouse::

She kept staring at Qiuckstrike.  Just something about him that stirred a 
partially deleted memory.  She knew him from somewhere. Her logic circuits 
wanted her to run away from the doorway.  Her spark told her different.  
This was driving her crazy.  She wanted to talk to him in the worst way.  
But something was holding her back.  She took two steps towards Quickstrike 
and stopped.  She shook her head and truned around and walked back down the 
hallway towards her quarters.
"I must be losing my mental circuits or something."
